.. activecode:: er1002
   
    Write a program that spins a "Magic Eight Ball."
    The user thinks of a question and then runs the program.
    The program randomly chooses one of eight "yes/no/maybe" answers (you can make these up).
    The program then asks the user if they want to go again, and responds appropriately.
